title: chaos_stotch
author: chaos_stotch
content: Hello my fellow developers.Over the last year, I have been making some money working on developing small automation applications with python.However, I wanted to earn more money, so I learned node, reactJS, threeJS and learned to create beautiful websites in the last few months.Meanwhile I'm dying to get a single customer even if I really try.Can anyone shed some light on what I should do to see more money? I accept any type of tip, but my focus is to continue working as an independent developer.Mainly in attracting customersThis is my website: chaos-stotch.github.io/ so this is the level of beauty I can do hehehe
